{"tid":702374,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴：瑞典冇我冇晒壓力","createTime":"2018-06-15T00:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T16:28:42.000Z","uid":32938,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"923a579d2d421a9681924daa1fde19d6cad13b25","tid":702374,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:13:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=51ef0f47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】伊巴謙莫域認為，沒有其在陣，整隊瑞典的壓力和預期都將會減少，呼籲國家隊在沒壓力下盡情享受世界盃比賽，踢出最佳水平。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）最終也沒有重返國家隊，為瑞典出戰今屆世盃，該名前瑞典國腳認為沒有他在陣，亦並非壞事：「我認為瑞典在沒有我的情況下，將會承受較少壓力，因為若我在陣，己隊就會被預期勝出一切。現在好好享受世界盃吧，沒有壓力的，因為我已不在陣。」"},{"pid":"1c9b64d4906226d5244f17d15e8dac5456e0631f","tid":702374,"uid":13395,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入選左就會話有我增強士氣"},{"pid":"ea36377bd6e5209b0b9fa1b40c7e61e6e9be0adf","tid":702374,"uid":8883,"like":98,"dislike":4,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:17:28.000Z","msg":"佢都真係幾撚煩<br />\n祝福就祝福啦<br />\n又要拉埋自己影響力黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0630590d59c2d62d0c334f0f8a27fbdce127e2c","tid":702374,"uid":78971,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"「冇我都冇機會爭冠軍<br />\n盡情享受就算」"},{"pid":"dc9d0771c63a5adcba200a588ae99455e95fda2e","tid":702374,"uid":72321,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:18:40.000Z","msg":"咁佢又錯唔曬"},{"pid":"ba70d73e6dfdcc5e55a8e684b38f256ff4e91937","tid":702374,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0630590d59c2d62d0c334f0f8a27fbdce127e2c","tid":702374,"uid":78971,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"「冇我都冇機會爭冠軍<br />\n盡情享受就算」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15